Package de.th_nuernberg.bluehome.RuleProcessObjects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionObject
    ActionObject is used in BlueHome Devices to trigger actions on the hardware.
    RPC
    RPC (RuleProcessConstants) Contains all defines for Rule Process
    RuleObject
    RuleObject is used to descripe dependencies between SourceObject and ActionObject.
    SourceObject
    Source Object is the Object that is generated when an interrupt on a BlueHome Device occours.
